rows.label: qst100601_msg0001
rows.name:
Momo?! Are you one of
Bahn's lackeys, mo?!

rows.label: qst100601_msg0002
rows.name:
Mo? It's all of you, mo!
Long time no see, mo.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm currently investigating
Bahn's assets as a member of
the Special Audit Bureau, mo.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0004
rows.name:
The Special Audit Bureau keeps an
eye out for illegal logistics and
exchanges of money and goods, mo.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0005
rows.name:
Bahn's assets were confiscated
due to the artificial Blade
facility incident, but...

rows.label: qst100601_msg0006
rows.name:
I was searching Bahn's room
to see if there were any
more hidden assets, mo.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0007
rows.name:
That's when I found this treasure
chest, but I can't open it, mo!

rows.label: qst100601_msg0008
rows.name:
There's no key-like
thing... and no switch...

rows.label: qst100601_msg0009
rows.name:
It's an important piece of evidence,
but I can't do anything without
knowing what's inside, mo...

rows.label: qst100601_msg0010
rows.name:
It would be a great help if
you could say that, mo.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0011
rows.name:
How can it be opened, mo? Please
teach me for future reference, mo!

rows.label: qst100601_msg0501
rows.name:
Please open the treasure chest with
the power of a Blade-san, mo!
